OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney reports on how the North West
OL,8,Fhas been affected by the extreme
OL,9,Fweather
OL,11,FTemperature records were broken in the
OL,12,FNorth West on Thursday as the region
OL,13,Fcontinued to bake on day four of the
OL,14,Fheatwave.
OL,16,FIn Crosby, the mercury reached 34
OL,17,Fdegrees, setting a new record for June
OL,18,Ftemperatures in the regions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
