OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FAn amber heat warning was still in
OL,7,Fplace across much of the North West as
OL,8,Fdisruption continued on the transport
OL,9,Fnetworks.
OL,11,FMeanwhile Fire and Rescue services
OL,12,Freiterated calls for people to stay
OL,13,Fsafe near open water after four people
OL,14,Fdrowned in the region during a warm
OL,15,Fspell last month.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
