OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FSome schools took the decision to
OL,7,Fclose because of the extreme heat. One
OL,8,FNorthwich headteacher called for a
OL,9,Fnational strategy to make it more
OL,10,Fclear for schools on when to close and
OL,11,Fhow to mitigate rising temperatures.
OL,13,FLindsay Cade, head of Hartford Primary
OL,14,Fschool said: "This is going to happen
OL,15,Fyear on year now, it's not going to go
OL,16,Faway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,F"Do we have this frenzy every year
OL,7,Fabout deciding what to do or do we
OL,8,Fhave a national strategy, where we
OL,9,Fthink more about do we change the
OL,10,Fbuildings, do we have air con, do we
OL,11,Fchange the start and finish times of
OL,12,Fthe day when we get to an extreme
OL,13,Ftemperature as we've seen this week?"
OL,15,FTeachers and pupils at Hartford
OL,16,Fprimary in Northwich talk to ITV News:
OL,18,FPupils at Hartford Primary have kept
OL,19,Fcool by putting feet into trays of
OL,20,Fwater, and wearing PE kits instead of
OL,21,Fthe usual school uniform.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
