OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FMany people took advantage of air-
OL,7,Fconditioned offices to escape the
OL,8,Fheat, as experts warned many homes are
OL,9,Fill-equipped to deal with an ever
OL,10,Fchanging climate.
OL,12,FAt Salford University, their energy
OL,13,Fhome lab provides unique testing
OL,14,Fenvironments where researchers and
OL,15,Findustry experts can simulate weather
OL,16,Fconditions and trial new housing
OL,17,Ftechnologies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
