PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FProfessor of Energy and Buildings at
OL,7,FSalford University, Lubo Jankovic,
OL,8,Fsaid homes have traditionally been
OL,9,Fdesigned for heating, and that is the
OL,10,Fproblem.
OL,12,FProf Lubo Jankovic said heat pumps
OL,13,Foperating in reverse could be a useful
OL,14,Fsolution:
OL,16,FFor those without homes, the extreme
OL,17,Ftemperatures have caused their own
OL,18,Fproblems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
