CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782411503
OL,3,CTemperature record broken as the North
OL,4,CWest bakes in heatwave
OL,6,FThe Mustard Tree homeless charity in
OL,7,FManchester has been appealing for
OL,8,Fthings like suncream and summer
OL,9,Fclothes to help support the homeless
OL,10,Fthrough the scorching temperatures.
OL,12,FJack Barton from the Mustard Tree
OL,13,Fhomeless charity said they've been
OL,14,Fappealing for specific donations:
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
